					<description><![CDATA[<p>Oxylabs Raises $130M to Accelerate AI Data Infrastructure Lithuania-based web data infrastructure company Oxylabs has received $130 million in funding from private equity firm Warburg Pincus. The investment values the</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/oxylabs-raises-130m-to-expand-ai-data-infrastructure-platform/" data-wpel-link="internal">Oxylabs Raises $130M to Expand AI Data Infrastructure Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><b>Oxylabs Raises $130M to Accelerate AI Data Infrastructure</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Lithuania-based web data infrastructure company Oxylabs has received $130 million in funding from private equity firm Warburg Pincus. The investment values the company at $3.6 billion and marks the first outside capital since its launch in 2015.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The capital came by way of Warburg Pincus Capital Solutions Founders Fund. With this latest influx of cash, the company expects to accelerate the expansion of its product roadmap, bolster its tech stack, and further pursue strategic acquisitions. </span></p>
<h2><b>AI Growth Creates Demand for Live Web Data</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Oxylabs has been providing web data infrastructure which empowers businesses to obtain public internet data at scale. Technology from the company, a producer of web intelligence data infrastructure, supports artificial intelligence advancements with its real-time capabilities. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">It provides real-time information for large language models, autonomous AI agents, and retrieval-augmented generation applications. It handles billions of web requests each day and holds in excess of 160 patents for its technology.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">E-commerce firms, the cybersecurity sector and market research entities have utilized Oxylabs’ infrastructure, including to gather competitor pricing information, analyze consumer purchasing patterns, track cybersecurity threats and identify fraudulent practices.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Vytautas Savickas, chief executive of Oxylabs, said he can clearly see future AI relying on real-time internet information rather than static datasets. He argued the company has positioned itself to serve this emerging market over several years.</span></p>
<h2><b>Funding Supports Product Expansion and Strategic Acquisitions</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_203490" style="width: 1322px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203490" class="size-full wp-image-203490" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Oxylabs-2.png" alt="Illustration of AI data infrastructure, global web intelligence networks, and strategic technology partnerships supporting enterprise AI growth and infrastructure expansion." width="1312" height="736" /><p id="caption-attachment-203490" class="wp-caption-text">Investment in AI data infrastructure is accelerating product innovation, strategic acquisitions, and global partnerships, strengthening the foundation for enterprise AI while reinforcing Europe&#8217;s role in the next generation of intelligent data platforms. Source: Created by Ventureburn.</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The investment comes on top of increased demand for AI data infrastructure, an area where the latest deal allows Oxylabs to improve its competitive offering. Alongside product enhancements, the company intends to complete further acquisitions and strategic partnerships. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">To date, Oxylabs has grown through a pair of add-ons: in Webshare in 2022 and ScrapingBee in 2025. The latest deal will fuel these further initiatives and help to deepen the company&#8217;s technology capabilities.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Warburg Pincus said Oxylabs has emerged as a significant player in the web intelligence landscape and noted that the investment underscores increasing trust in European tech players creating the underlying infrastructure for the global AI revolution. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The latest move deepens Warburg Pincus&#8217; engagement with the technology sector in Lithuania, a country in which it also has an investment in Nord Security, another prominent tech company founded at the Tesonet startup accelerator.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: <a href="https://ventureburn.com/kraken-technology-raises-175m-to-expand-maritime-defence-systems/" data-wpel-link="internal">Kraken Technology Raises $175M to Expand Maritime Defence Systems</a></span></p>
<h2><b>Company Focuses on Responsible Web Data Collection</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">As web scraping grows alongside AI development, the industry continues to face increased regulatory attention. Questions surrounding ethical </span><a href="https://ori.hhs.gov/education/products/n_illinois_u/datamanagement/dctopic.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">data collection</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> and residential proxy networks have encouraged providers to place greater emphasis on compliance and transparency.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Oxylabs says responsible data collection remains a core part of its business strategy. The company helped establish an ethical web data initiative and has introduced compliance audits through its trust centre to strengthen customer confidence.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company believes demand for real-time internet data will continue to increase as AI agents become more widely adopted across industries. Oxylabs aims to position itself as a critical technology provider for the next generation of artificial intelligence applications.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">To stay updated on crypto venture capital funding and market trends, visit our </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/category/news/venture-capital/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">venture capital news section</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> for more insights.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/oxylabs-raises-130m-to-expand-ai-data-infrastructure-platform/" data-wpel-link="internal">Oxylabs Raises $130M to Expand AI Data Infrastructure Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
