					<description><![CDATA[<p>The competitive arena is officially open as Binance Wallet unrolls its latest high-stakes token event on the early-stage listing platform. The Binance Alpha Unibase (UB) Trading Competition is live, offering</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/binance-alpha-ub-trading-competition/" data-wpel-link="internal">Binance Alpha Trading Competition Is Live: Trade Unibase (UB) and Share Massive Rewards!</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The competitive arena is officially open as <a href="https://accounts.binance.com/register?ref=O0BTS35V" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external">Binance</a> Wallet unrolls its latest high-stakes token event on the early-stage listing platform. The <b>Binance Alpha Unibase (UB) Trading Competition</b> is live, offering a premier opportunity for Web3 traders to test market strategies on the newly listed UB token.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The tournament is organized into two back-to-back promotion periods to maintain a highly active leaderboard:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>1st UB Trading Competition Promotion Period:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> July 8, 2026, 13:00 to July 15, 2026, 13:00 (UTC)</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>2nd UB Trading Competition Promotion Period:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> July 15, 2026, 13:00 to July 22, 2026, 13:00 (UTC)</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This guide breaks down the updated scoring rules, multiplier frameworks, and exact platform steps needed to lock in your token rewards. Ensure your wallet is ready and your Binance Alpha Points are checked before the trading window closes.</span></p>
<p><b><i>More Active Trading Programs: </i></b><a href="https://ventureburn.com/binance-traders-league-season-3-sent/" data-wpel-link="internal"><b><i>Join the Binance Traders League Season 3 To Share Rewards</i></b></a></p>
<h2><b>Competition Details &amp; Reward Structure</b></h2>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Total Prize Pool:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 1,050,600 UB tokens (distributed over two periods)</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Reward Per Eligible User:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 510 UB tokens flat</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Eligible Trading Infrastructure:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Binance Wallet (Keyless) or Binance Alpha</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Minimum Volume Target:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> No volume caps per user</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Participants are ranked based on their total cumulative spot purchase volume of UB tokens during the active promotion period. Note that selling volume is completely excluded from the leaderboard calculations. The top 2,060 purchasing accounts per round are guaranteed an equal split of that period&#8217;s allocated pool.</span></p>
<h3><b>Multiplier Systems</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To reward early execution and consistent participation, Binance uses two scoring boosters:</span></p>
<ol>
<li><b> Early Bird Boost Multiplier</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Trades executed on earlier days receive a higher volume multiplier. The formula is: Daily Effective Trading Volume = Actual Trading Volume * Early Bird Boost Multiplier</span></li>
</ol>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><b>Trading Day</b></td>
<td><b>Eligible Date and Time (UTC)</b></td>
<td><b>Multiplier</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 1</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 08, 13:00 to Jul 09, 13:00 &amp; Jul 15, 13:00 to Jul 16, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 2</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 09, 13:00 to Jul 10, 13:00 &amp; Jul 16, 13:00 to Jul 17, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 3</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 10, 13:00 to Jul 11, 13:00 &amp; Jul 17, 13:00 to Jul 18, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.8x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 4</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 11, 13:00 to Jul 12, 13:00 &amp; Jul 18, 13:00 to Jul 19, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.8x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 5</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 12, 13:00 to Jul 13, 13:00 &amp; Jul 19, 13:00 to Jul 20, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.5x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 6</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 13, 13:00 to Jul 14, 13:00 &amp; Jul 20, 13:00 to Jul 21, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.3x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 7</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 14, 13:00 to Jul 15, 13:00 &amp; Jul 21, 13:00 to Jul 22, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.0x</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<ol start="2">
<li><b> Rising Trader Boost Multiplier</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> If you have won rewards in fewer than 3 historical Binance Wallet Alpha competitions, you qualify as a &#8220;Rising Trader&#8221; and receive a </span><b>1.2x boost</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> on your actual volume. This is capped at a maximum of 5,000 USDT in volume.</span></li>
</ol>
<p><b>Scoring Equation (Plain Text Format):</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Effective Trading Volume = (Actual Trading Volume * Early Bird Boost Multiplier) + min(Actual Trading Volume, Remaining Rising Trader Boost Cap) * Rising Trader Boost</span></p>
<h2><b>How to Participate</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To successfully log your purchase turnover points on the tournament leaderboard, follow these exact setup milestones inside the app:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Step 1 &#8211; Registration Opt-In:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Open your Binance App, Go to </span><b>Binance Wallet</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, navigate to the event landing page, and click the </span><b>[Join]</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> button. Trading volume only counts </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">after</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;"> you have clicked join.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Step 2 &#8211; Prepare Your Wallet:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Ensure your app is updated and your Binance Wallet (Keyless) is properly created and backed up.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Step 3 &#8211; Trade:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Execute your UB purchase orders via the Binance Wallet (Keyless) interface or through the Binance Alpha dashboard.</span></li>
</ul>
<h2><b>Important Rules &amp; Disqualification Policies</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Before organizing your market orders, review these critical operational guardrails:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Only trades routed through </span><b>Binance Wallet (Keyless)</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> or the </span><b>Binance Alpha</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> tab are tracked. External third-party dApp browser transactions are invalid.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Token bridging transactions and &#8220;Alpha-to-Alpha&#8221; pair swaps are excluded from volume scoring.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Reward Claims:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Winners must claim their UB token rewards via their Binance Alpha or Binance Wallet account </span><b>within 14 days</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> of the distribution window opening on July 31, 2026, or the tokens will be forfeited.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Anti-Fraud Protocols:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Binance maintains a zero-tolerance policy against wash trading, bulk account registrations, self-dealing, or volume manipulation. Any detected malicious behavior triggers immediate, permanent disqualification from the tournament.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><b><i>More Earn Programs:</i></b><a href="https://ventureburn.com/binance-alpha-nexus-trading-competition-is-live-trade-nex-and-share-massive-token-rewards/" data-wpel-link="internal"> <b><i>Join the Binance Alpha NEX Trading Competition</i></b></a></p>
