<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">How Does Crypto Prop Trading Differ From Traditional Prop Trading?</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Traditional prop firms (such as on Wall Street) demand that you have a degree, pass interviews, and physically work in an office. They pay a salary plus a bonus. Any person with an internet connection can access crypto prop firms. There are often no background checks and no interviews. </span></p>
