<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Limited Risk:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> You can only lose the challenge fee.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Advanced Tools:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Many crypto prop firms offer traders access to advanced tools.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>24/7 Markets: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Crypto allows you to trade weekends and holidays.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Payouts in Crypto:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Fast settlements in USDT/USDC.</span></li>
